{"tid":1641274,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[黑色帶風警告] 立場出左篇唔好舉青天白日滿地紅旗嘅文 就即刻多左成班人帶風話唔好舉旗","createTime":"2019-10-09T09:43:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-10T04:45:53.000Z","uid":270506,"like":13,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"118fc2613369911acdf9c2e6394a5a5e926b1069","tid":1641274,"uid":270506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T09:43:31.000Z","msg":"雙十係慶祝中華民國國慶，唔舉中華民國國旗咁唔通舉咩！同埋大家睇下立場fb 嘅留言，篇文係比人屌緊<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/710476795704610/posts/2515425858543019?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F710476795704610%2Fposts%2F2515425858543019%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=B%2BAVUFxUUUF%2FouYpVm7lNmipy2YcCk4ac690EPkq9Sw%3D&h=1fe3e34c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/710476795704610/posts/2515425858543019?sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n各位小心被人帶風，似乎共匪真係好驚聽日全港旗海，所以搵五毛寫左篇聲稱已經民主化嘅中華民國係極權體制嘅帶風文叫人唔好舉旗。大家要有批判思考，唔好比人帶風！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iVjVhXi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiVjVhXi.png&h=35b7ab77&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2d41ac2ff6a8d673231da95ca3ad0bc8aa05f4b3","tid":1641274,"uid":292925,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T09:50:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7LLxkcZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7LLxkcZ.jpg&h=451596d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OyCr86j.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOyCr86j.jpg&h=f965c866&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9be31ae7d1823b95f86e8b63060fb7cf36efc866","tid":1641274,"uid":53610,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T09:52:38.000Z","msg":"見到一版幾個post，講埋啲嘢差唔多，標題又係乜抄車，請勿，求下你哋唔好，就知道三毛狗又吹緊風<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53e3c39db707ae58ec370e85db7fdd26e06eca07","tid":1641