br />\n基於黨「不等於」國。 如果説要「民主選舉」就必須接受黨「不等於」國的概念。 另一方面，中華民國亦「非在臺灣誕生」，「香港亦是誕生地之一」。"},{"pid":"9c51c2005ec1e20ae9bc4179ac174e6db07bf68e","tid":1641274,"uid":283494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T02:56:21.000Z","msg":"青天白日滿地紅旗係中共死穴,亦可connect到廢老<br />\n<br />\n出少少文宣同台灣朋友解釋一下便可"},{"pid":"24577d982feaeddc68f001f924adf810b04289de","tid":1641274,"uid":244607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T03:13:53.000Z","msg":"中共死穴<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/ok.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6efc326cfcbebe2187366a3fe0721cd93893a253","tid":1641274,"uid":109780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T03:15:02.000Z","msg":"舉青天白日滿地紅加美國旗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f65d5fbbed574586e122983ae0878386783225a4","tid":1641274,"uid":40748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T03:27:16.000Z","msg":"各有各做 兄弟爬山呀 係咪唔記得呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf2ad25bf9741237fedc52d4821edcf8bf1bd636","tid":1641274,"uid":40748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T03:28:30.000Z","msg":"唔好慢慢又嫌乜嫌物 唔好唔記得運動初心 肯為呢場運動做任何既野 都係正確"},{"pid":"f2e69efc3d712f0ded088d6264415019502f25de","tid":1641274,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T03:35:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47f5e1e8b299a84c7bdd99754993af3f12f644ef","tid":1641274,"uid":244607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T04:45:53.000Z","msg":"推"}]}